dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours, hachures, form lines, and spot heights. Map series of Asia Minor (Turkey) showing roads, railways, religious buildings, chief towns, vilayet, sanjak, kaza or nahie, and international boundaries. Izmid sheet is a color reprinted edition of 1925. Relief shown by contours.Includes a glossary in Turkish and English. Includes reference table in Turkish and English. Map sheet are named but not numbered. Set of 32 sheets. Relief shown by hachures, form lines, and spot heights.  Includes glossary of terms in Turkish and English.
dct_creator_sm: Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section
